theorem Topology.closure_interior_eq_compl_interior_closure_compl
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    closure (interior A) = (interior (closure (Aᶜ)))ᶜ := by
  -- Start from the existing relation between the complements.
  have h :=
    Topology.compl_closure_interior_eq_interior_closure_compl (A := A)
  -- Take complements of both sides and simplify.
  simpa [Set.compl_compl] using congrArg Set.compl h

theorem Set.compl_compl {α : Type*} (s : Set α) : sᶜᶜ = s := by
  simpa using (compl_compl s)
